href="https://mizar.uwb.edu.pl/version/current/html/field_16.html#K5">field_16:def 6</fr:link></fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> be a field of characteristic <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[p>0]]></fr:tex>. The <html:dfn
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Frobenius Morphism</html:dfn> is
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\begin {split}\phi \colon &\mathbb {F}\to \mathbb {F}\\ &x\mapsto  x^{p}\end {split}]]></fr:tex>
Moreover, this is a field morphism.</fr:p>
 
   
